animate_daily

library(EpiTrans)
R = Rj(t = dengue$date, x = dengue$long, y = dengue$lat)
dengue$Rj = R$Rj
dengue = dengue[dengue$date > as.Date("2007-09-15") & dengue$date < as.Date("2007-10-15"),]
plot_points(x = dengue$long, y = dengue$lat, Rj = dengue$Rj, basemap = Taiwan, bnd = bnd)
animate_daily(x = dengue$long, y = dengue$lat,t = dengue$date,dt = 7)

animate_daily(x = dengue$long, y = dengue$lat,t = dengue$date,dt = 7,Rj = dengue$Rj)
